Mayo, horseradish, and ketchup! Sour cream, and McCormick's roasted garlic and herb! Honey, mustard, and hot sauce. Then there is the steak itself. I like mine still kicking, while my wife likes what I would call shoe leather. When it comet to cooking; What I like; you may hate.
